<para style="q1">

<verse number="70" style="v" />He chose David, his servant,</para>

<para style="q1">and took him from the sheepfolds.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="71" style="v" />He took him from following the ewes with their young, and he brought him</para>

<para style="q1">to be shepherd of Jacob, his people, and of Israel, his heritage.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="72" style="v" />David shepherded them with the integrity of his heart,</para>

<para style="q1">and he guided them with the skill of his hands.</para>
